skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: times table quiz
des: The Times Table Quiz skill allows you to test your knowledge of the times table with a set of 10 randomly chosen questions. You can test yourself with a quiz for all the Times Tables between zero and twelve, or you can test yourself on a specific Times Table. The skill will keep you up to date with your score.
